{
  "id": "RAW_2f1991a0",
  "title": "Claude Code 开源了代码简化 Agent，千年“屎山”代码终于有救了！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651271147&idx=2&sn=a2becd0deac1389aa8f084a94c802ffe",
  "date": "2026-01-11 02:15:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 | 冬梅 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code 开源了代码简化 Agent，千年“屎山”代码终于有救了！</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code 的创建者刚刚</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源了</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">他团队用来清理大型混乱 PR 的内部代码简化代理。它</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">旨在</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">长时间编码结束后运行，在不改变程序行为的前提下降低复杂度。该功能由 Claude Code 团队</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">分享，现在可通过官方插件试用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">开源地址：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #888888;font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/code-simplifier\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins/code-simplifier</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503787460\" data-ratio=\"1.2657407407407408\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=99d1d773&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMRB3wYvrtvgpo6X3q7rDiaSqXOPDkV2Q9IVH5RkSlYETH71Y5wHKjbkSW8ED74DVzpoSsIkhUZpEg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，究竟什么是代码简化代理（code-simplifier agent）？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方给出的介绍非常直白：这个智能体专门用于在</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">长时间编码之后自动简化代码结构、减少冗余，并提高整体可读性与一致性</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，同时严格遵循“绝不改变程序行为”的原则。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503787456\" data-ratio=\"0.3420138888888889\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"576\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7c6e6ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMRB3wYvrtvgpo6X3q7rDiaSzPct7V4uUjad7qQPj5UqPuMZlGiaQBFUHFT7F2aLZPJuns2Hlxbc4sA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它可以看作是一个“智能重构助手”——具备约等于一名多年经验工程师的职责，即在确保正确性的前提下，通过自动化方式：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">提炼嵌套复杂、逻辑混乱的代码</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">消除冗余变量、重复逻辑与不必要的条件判断</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">清理过度注释或无效注释</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">统一样式、简化函数结构</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">根据现有开源的文件模板（code-simplifier.md），这个代理会接收当前代码库以及上下文信息，然后基于内部设定的专业角色和行为规范，往往会生成一套更符合清晰度与可维护性标准的代码结构。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发者该如何使用这项功能？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 已将代码简化代理发布在官方插件市场中，用户可以通过以下步骤安装：</span></p>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">/plugin marketplace update claude-plugins-official</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">/plugin install code-simplifier</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装成功后，可在 Claude Code 的交互式会话中启用该代理，让其在长时间编码或接收复杂 PR 时运行，以自动产出简化后的版本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一点对于处理大型遗留项目特别有意义，因为手工重构往往耗时耗力，而简单的自动化工具又无法保证行为不变——code-simplifier agent 的出现，在一定程度上填补了这一领域的缺口。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;border-bottom: 2px solid #00b38b;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;background-size: 55px auto;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20260111070536_abbfdf01&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">网友怎么看？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 X 平台，有网友认为，这款 Agent 非常实用，并建议其他工具也具备这样的功能。他提议道：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">“太实用了！我觉得所有智能代理工具都应该具备这个功能。每次提交 PR 之前，我都要手动告诉代理清理代码，严格遵循 DRY、SOLID、KISS 等原则，避免不必要的间接性和过度复杂化。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503787457\" data-ratio=\"0.2564814814814815\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=364a3433&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMRB3wYvrtvgpo6X3q7rDiaSc1V5SmopU2icvvZNBeqEmGYtw7b2BsRHDzcMbrqKQibNic9XY7cmwlqRg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">不少网友肯定了 Claude 团队这次开源的行为，认为这个工具非常实用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503787459\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=77c9b49d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMRB3wYvrtvgpo6X3q7rDiaSygsJsDKgB09flNJic0BOKfy02kt4yTrpkaeAqE1qCK2ug2G09xoBJ7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有网友表扬了 Claude Code 团队，认为他们发布这样的工具比保密更能在竞争中建立优势。</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“开源这个真是太棒了。大多数组织都会把好东西藏起来。说实话，发布这样的工具比保守秘密更能建立竞争优势。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503787458\" data-ratio=\"0.13425925925925927\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d1686cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMRB3wYvrtvgpo6X3q7rDiaSuicmMFolRibCC2oQyibzJok9zVVAevx9Uwe4ia4fwP5lqLTxqd2l9L6n8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有网友呼吁 Claude Code 团队别再藏着掖着了，把所有内部技能都开源吧！</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503787461\" data-ratio=\"0.13425925925925927\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31f46852&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMRB3wYvrtvgpo6X3q7rDiaSwNWwibvE11CvPcqibBZ7fSknFGfTicP84PhNEKtkjHKialibicby1US7vP3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Reddit 上，也有网友表示以前没有这个功能时是走了一些弯路，希望这次能好点。</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我之前让 Claude 意识到它的代码变得太复杂了，它说要简化一下……你猜怎么着？它开始删除很多原本可以正常运行的代码，然后用一些空函数替换掉。希望这次能好点儿！反正我和 Git 打算试试。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #888888;\">参考链接：</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #888888;\"><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/ClaudeAI/comments/1q8h6oz/claude_code_creator_open_sources_the_internal/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/ClaudeAI/comments/1q8h6oz/claude_code_creator_open_sources_the_internal/</a></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Claude Code 团队开源了一款 AI 代码简化 Agent，能够在不改变程序行为的前提下，自动清理和优化代码，缓解“屎山”代码问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Claude Code 团队开源了一款 AI 代码简化 Agent，能够在不改变程序行为的前提下，自动清理和优化代码，缓解“屎山”代码问题。",
  "summary": "文章报道了 Claude Code 团队开源其内部使用的代码简化 Agent，该工具旨在不改变程序行为的前提下，自动清理复杂、冗余的代码，提高代码可读性与一致性。文章详细介绍了该 Agent 的主要功能，包括提炼嵌套复杂代码、消除冗余变量和重复逻辑、清理注释、统一样式等。同时，文章提供了安装和使用该 Agent 的步骤，并提及了其在处理大型遗留项目中的潜在价值。文末引用了网友对该工具的积极评价，认为其高度实用，并建议其他 AI 工具也应具备类似功能，甚至呼吁 Claude 团队开源更多内部工具。也提及了部分网友对 AI 工具的谨慎态度。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Claude Code 团队开源内部代码简化 Agent，旨在自动化代码重构。",
      "explanation": "这款 Agent 能够帮助开发者在不改变代码逻辑的前提下，自动简化复杂结构、消除冗余、统一代码风格，有效提升代码质量和可维护性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该 Agent 是“智能重构助手”，具备多年经验工程师的职责。",
      "explanation": "其功能包括提炼复杂逻辑、清除冗余变量、清理注释、统一样式等，特别适用于处理大型遗留项目，弥补了手动重构耗时和简单自动化工具可靠性不足的空白。"
    },
    {
      "point": "用户可通过官方插件在 Claude Code 环境中安装并使用该 Agent。",
      "explanation": "Anthropic 已将其发布在官方插件市场，开发者可以通过简单的命令安装，并在交互式会话中启用，以便在复杂编码任务后自动生成优化后的代码。"
    },
    {
      "point": "市场反响积极，认为开源此类工具促进了技术生态发展。",
      "explanation": "网友普遍认为该 Agent 高度实用，呼吁更多 AI 工具集成类似功能，并赞扬 Claude 团队的开源精神，认为这比封闭保守更能建立竞争优势。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
